    <string name="info_dialog_title">What is BMI?</string>
    <string name="info_dialog_message">Body Mass Index (BMI) is a simple measure that uses your height and weight to work out if your weight is healthy.\n\n📐 Formula:\nBMI = weight (kg) ÷ height² (m²)\n\n📊 Categories:\n• Below 18.5 — Underweight\n• 18.5 – 24.9 — Normal Weight\n• 25.0 – 29.9 — Overweight\n• 30.0 and above — Obese\n\n⚠️ Note: BMI is a screening tool, not a diagnostic measure. Consult a healthcare professional for medical advice.</string>
    <string name="info_dialog_button">Got it</string>

